## 3. Dataset Construction
### 3.1 Dataset Scale
The training dataset consists of **2,003 instruction-response pairs**:
- **200 handcrafted core Q&As:** Foundational questions with direct scriptural citations.
- **2 boundary-definition pairs:** Explicit guidelines for permitted and forbidden outputs.
- **1,800 synthetically expanded Q&As:** Algorithmically generated coverage across all 66 books of the Bible.
